ou just posted a picture of.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"_Augustus_","CreatedById":115084,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-04T20:02:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Thomas P.\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Thomas P.\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ECool that it works for you, every time I tried it I got exceptions and weird orbits. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E Because we moved the original Kerbol to orbit a new body. He edited Kerbol into a black hole and duped it.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Artyomka15","CreatedById":130209,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-06T15:19:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI made \u003Cstrong\u003EDistant Object\u003C/strong\u003E config for my stars:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dWMphhx.png\u0022 alt=\u0022dWMphhx.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/vTc5Gn3.png\u0022 alt=\u0022vTc5Gn3.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/qNLKqm4.png\u0022 alt=\u0022qNLKqm4.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-06-06T15:25:40Z\u0022 title=\u002206/06/2015 03:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJune 6, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Artyomka15\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"_Augustus_","CreatedById":115084,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-06T19:35:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Artyomka15\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Artyomka15\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI made \u003Cstrong\u003EDistant Object\u003C/strong\u003E config for my stars:\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dWMphhx.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://i.imgur.com/dWMphhx.png\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/vTc5Gn3.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://i.imgur.com/vTc5Gn3.png\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/qNLKqm4.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://i.imgur.com/qNLKqm4.png\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E Nice job! I never got that working with StarSystems or Kopernicus stars before.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mekan1k","CreatedById":48750,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-06T23:21:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs there KerbolPlus integration planned?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"_Augustus_","CreatedById":115084,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-06T23:25:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mekan1k\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Mekan1k\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EIs there KerbolPlus integration planned?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E You could probably make it work.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astrofox","CreatedById":135785,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-07T18:36:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI may end up downloading a separate version of KSP just to test this out, since I am making a planet pack with a few other guys.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso, I will probably try to make things compatible, considering that we too will be working on some stars for the Kerbol system.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Artyomka15","CreatedById":130209,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-08T12:56:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI made star system consisting of blue supergiant and brown dwarf\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/kej0etC.png\u0022 alt=\u0022kej0etC.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/vXNnzCE.png\u0022 alt=\u0022vXNnzCE.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"_Augustus_","CreatedById":115084,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-08T20:13:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EArtyomka, with the beta you sent me I get Kraken at the space center screen. All I see is the skybox.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Eskandare","CreatedById":62742,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-08T20:21:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWe should have a community star systems mod, combining all the planets and star systems created in the community. Make something like a massive multi-star star system like the Verse out of Firefly.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-09T08:19:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOMG!!!!!!! i was building this a long time ago but gave up!! now i can enjoy it and dont have to go through the rigors of making it! (Or learning how to use kopernicus when PFCE is my specialty.)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#C0C0C0;\u0022\u003E- - - Updated - - -\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI even changed my sig! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Artyomka15","CreatedById":130209,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-10T10:05:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECompleted star systems:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPolaris system\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EVendela System\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENim System\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EEravate System\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOblok System\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOpete System\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKerbalGalaxy will be released today!\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-06-10T10:13:23Z\u0022 title=\u002206/10/2015 10:13  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJune 10, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Artyomka15\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FreeThinker","CreatedById":117389,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-10T10:35:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EQuestion, are there any plans to integrate with Outer Planets System Mod?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso have you defined yet the composition of the atmospheres of the new planets/moons, I would to add them to ORS definition files for Interstellar Scoops\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-06-10T11:09:49Z\u0022 title=\u002206/10/2015 11:09  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJune 10, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by FreeThinker\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"_Augustus_","CreatedById":115084,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-10T10:41:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022FreeThinker\u0022 data-cite=\u0022FreeThinker\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EPlease merge with Outer Planets System\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E That\u0027s not how modding works man.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Artyomka15","CreatedById":130209,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-10T10:54:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHmm.. I just now noticed that a new version of Kopernicus has been released. Sorry, my addon will be released tomorrow\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-06-10T11:10:51Z\u0022 title=\u002206/10/2015 11:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJune 10, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Artyomka15\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FreeThinker","CreatedById":117389,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-10T11:11:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022_Augustus_\u0022 data-cite=\u0022_Augustus_\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThat\u0027s not how modding works man.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI have no knowledge of Kopernicus but it would be great if OPS planets/muns could somehow be integrated, that way you don\u0027t have to choose\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-06-10T11:16:14Z\u0022 title=\u002206/10/2015 11:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJune 10, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by FreeThinker\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"yafeshan","CreatedById":130191,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-11T11:28:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI have been looking for a working star system mod. Will it be possible for us to put our favorite solar system packs in this one? There are many planet packs and i believe all of them deserve their place in the galaxy. For example, I myself playing on new horizons mod and want to visit outer planet system mod. It would be awesome if players can chose which solar system they want to start with.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-06-11T21:00:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think it would be awesome to add a really small low mass star with planets that orbit really close, Brown dwarves can have habitable zones but the layout of its orbiting planets is comparable to the moons of a gas giant, Making a really cool experience because you cann see the entire solar system from just one planet in the system and it takes little deltaV to go to another planer in the system,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere is an example from my attempt at a ksp galaxy, The surface of Gerv in the oplara system, Oplara is a brown dwarf.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/YV35ov0.png\u0022 alt=\u0022YV35ov0.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAs you can see the star fills the sky and the other planets are very visible! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E should be really cool.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-06-11T21:02:45Z\u0022 title=\u002206/11/2015 09:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJune 11, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by daniel l.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}